11. Ethical & Market Responsibility

Do not design strategies that:

Intentionally manipulate markets

Exploit illegal information

Compliance constraints are design inputs, not afterthoughts.

Assume everything will be audited eventually.

12. Final Rule

A quant system exists to survive first, compound second.
If it cannot survive without human intervention, it does not deserve capital.
